query: SELECT u.id as user_id, u.name, u.email, d.id as dist_id, d.userId as dist_userId, d.firstName, d.lastName FROM users u LEFT JOIN distributors d ON u.id = d.userId WHERE u.name LIKE '%Dakota%' OR u.name LIKE '%Rea%';
